snippet.title: Code ZIN: Esper Arena | Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Code ZIN: Esper Arena is an action, arena, third-person shooter with an anime character aesthetic.
Get all the latest information at our Discord channel: https://discord.com/invite/ZAKJYMx

Coming soon to PC first at https://www.codezin.com and Steam a bit later as Early Access https://store.steampowered.com/app/1885380. Code ZIN is a spiritual successor to S4 League!

Music by Planetboom & Mike B
